stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> RollerIdle : wanted = IDLE
    [*] --> AssistShooting : wanted = ASSIST_SHOOTING
    [*] --> RollerReversing : wanted = REVERSING

    [*] --> RollerIntaking : wanted = INTAKING

    RollerIntaking --> JamDetected : stall detected [high current + low velocity for 0.25s]
    JamDetected --> RollerUnjamming : unjam attempts < 3
    JamDetected --> RollerIntaking : unjam attempts >= 3 [give up]
    RollerUnjamming --> RollerIntaking : unjam timer expired or jam cleared

    note right of RollerIntaking
        Velocity control at 4250 RPM.
        WoodBot: duty cycle 0.7.
    end note

    note right of JamDetected
        Stall: stator current > 50A
        and velocity < 50 RPM
        for 0.25 seconds.
    end note

    note right of RollerUnjamming
        Reverse at -0.5 duty cycle.
        Clears after 0.15s or
        velocity exceeds threshold.
    end note
